OL,6,FWatch Kaf Okpattah's report.
OL,8,FThe father of schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,9,Fwho was murdered in a row over a teddy
OL,10,Fbear has said the conviction of her
OL,11,Fkiller is a "message" that violence
OL,12,Fagainst young women "will not go
OL,13,Funanswered".
