OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FElianne's father Michael Andam,
OL,7,Fspeaking outside the Old Bailey
OL,8,Ffollowing the conviction of Hassan
OL,9,FSentamu, 18, on Thursday, said: "The
OL,10,Fverdict today is the first step
OL,11,Ftowards justice for Elianne, but also
OL,12,Fa message that violence and knife
OL,13,Fcrime, especially towards young women,
OL,14,Fwill not go unanswered.
OL,16,F"Today, we choose not to dwell on the
OL,17,Fpain of the trial, but instead to
OL,18,Fhonour Elianne's memory."
