OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FHe also said: "Her death has left a
OL,7,Fvoid in our lives that can never be
OL,8,Ffilled."
OL,10,FHassan Sentamu, 18, had a history of
OL,11,Fattacking girls and carrying knives
OL,12,Fbefore he stabbed the popular
OL,13,Fschoolgirl in the neck outside the
OL,14,FWhitgift centre in Croydon, south-east
OL,15,FLondon.
OL,17,FAt Sentamu's trial, the prosecution
OL,18,Fclaimed the teenager had reacted to
OL,19,Fbeing splashed with water the day
OL,20,Fbefore and had lashed out at Elianne
OL,21,Fin a fit of "white hot" rage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
