OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FProsecutor Alex Chalk KC said: "He was
OL,7,Fangry on September 27, having brooded
OL,8,Fon the insult and he took the knife to
OL,9,Fthe scene to reassert dominance.
OL,11,F"He exacted vengeance on a young girl
OL,12,Fclearly running away from him and
OL,13,Fposing no threat."
OL,15,FAmid the public shock and outcry at
OL,16,Fthe killing, rap star Stormzy joined
OL,17,Fmembers of the community at a
OL,18,Fcandlelit vigil for Elianne in October
OL,19,F2023. Elianne aspired to become a
OL,20,Fhuman rights lawyer.
