OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FFollowing a three-week Old Bailey
OL,7,Ftrial a jury found Sentamu, from New
OL,8,FAddington, near Croydon, guilty of
OL,9,Fmurder by a majority of 10 to two and
OL,10,Funanimously guilty of possession of a
OL,11,Fblade.
OL,13,FThere were shouts of "yes" and
OL,14,F"murderer" from the public gallery as
OL,15,Fthe jury delivered the verdicts after
OL,16,Fdeliberating for 11 hours and 42
OL,17,Fminutes.
