OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FSentamu leaned against the front of
OL,7,Fthe dock crying and wiping his eyes as
OL,8,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb thanked and
OL,9,Fdischarged the jurors.
OL,11,FAdjourning sentencing until March 13
OL,12,Ffor reports, the senior judge told the
OL,13,Fteenager: "I understand you must be
OL,14,Fvery shocked and take time to get used
OL,15,Fto what has happened."
OL,17,FThree dock officers supported Sentamu
OL,18,Fas he was led down to the cells.
