OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold schoolgirl Elianne Andam
OL,6,FPaying tribute to Elianne, the
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police officer, who led
OL,8,Fthe murder investigation, said: "What
OL,9,Fhas really stuck with me is that
OL,10,FElianne always did what she thought
OL,11,Fwas right and stood up for her friend.
OL,13,F"We heard from her family during the
OL,14,Fcourse of this investigation that
OL,15,FElianne wanted to be a human rights
OL,16,Flawyer.
OL,18,F"She was very passionate about singing
OL,19,Fand dancing. She was passionate about
OL,20,Fher church as well."
